---
title: Saucy Tomato Beef & Pork Meatballs with Brown Rice, Capsicum & Mint Yoghurt
description: Beef and pork meatballs become super scrumptious when coated in a tomato-capsicum sauce, mildly spiced and all on top
of a helping of brown rice, tossed through with spinach. A cooling yoghurt soothes everything and brings this delicious dish
to perfection.
